WOW! HUGE price drop. Move-in ready home on 1/2 acre lot: NEW roof 2021', replaced windows-2017', Updated to central air & heat pump 2022'. New Stainless Steel range & dishwasher 2022’. Both bathrooms feature updates. The Spacious kitchen with eat-in area is bright with white cabinetry and new light flooring. There are timeless original hardwoods throughout most of the home [no carpet]. Primary bedroom has an on-suite half bath & there are 2 addtl bedrooms & a full bath. Mudroom/laundry room off of the kitchen. Large covered deck and covered front porch are great to enjoy the Carolina seasons. 
**1200 sqft BUILDING/GARAGE with EXTRA SPACE.This property is a DREAM for the car enthusiast or hobbyists or convert to a possible ADU/AirBNB with city approval. [Don’t need the extra space? -RENT IT to supplement the mortgage]. *NO* Homeowners Assoc. Bring the RV, motorsports, Boat & more! 
Only 10 MILES to center city Charlotte. Nationally Ranked Butler Highschool!
